</div><ul class="entry-meta" data-type="simple:slash" data-id="kXJEVS" ><li class="meta-author"><a class="ct-meta-element-author" href="https://www.circuitstate.com/author/vishnumaiea/" title="Posts by Vishnu Mohanan" rel="author"><span>Vishnu Mohanan</span></a></li><li class="meta-date" ><time class="ct-meta-element-date" datetime="2025-10-12T11:07:09+05:30">12 October 2025</time></li></ul></article><article class="entry-card card-content post-14934 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-tutorials tag-microcontroller tag-stm tag-stm8 tag-stm8s-blue tag-stm8s103f3p6" data-reveal="bottom:no"><ul class="entry-meta" data-type="simple:slash" data-id="j0qilM" ><li class="meta-categories" data-type="pill"><a href="https://www.circuitstate.com/tutorials/" rel="tag" class="ct-term-18">Tutorials</a></li></ul><h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.circuitstate.com/tutorials/hello-world-with-serial-uart-learn-microcontroller-with-stm8s-tutorial-part-8/" rel="bookmark">Hello World with Serial UART : Learn Microcontroller with STM8S &#8211; Tutorial Part #8</a></h2><a class="ct-media-container boundless-image" href="https://www.circuitstate.com/tutorials/hello-world-with-serial-uart-learn-microcontroller-with-stm8s-tutorial-part-8/" aria-label="Hello World with Serial UART : Learn Microcontroller with STM8S &#8211; Tutorial Part #8"><img width="768" height="576" src="https://www.circuitstate.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/What-is-A-Microcontroller-Learn-Microcontroller-with-STM8S-Part-8-Hello-World-with-UART-Featured-Image-CIRCUITSTATE-Electronics-1-JPG-2-768x576.jpg" class="attachment-medium_large size-medium_large wp-post-image" alt="Learn Microcontroller with STM8S Part 8 Hello World with UART Featured Image by CIRCUITSTATE Electronics" loading="lazy" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.circuitstate.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/What-is-A-Microcontroller-Learn-Microcontroller-with-STM8S-Part-8-Hello-World-with-UART-Featured-Im